{"title":"短歌（两首）","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":2,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"短歌（两首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十二月十六"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十二月十六，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一个大喜日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席斯大林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相会在莫斯科。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们两大领袖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们握一下手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人齐发抖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们好喜欢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们两大领袖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是和平的柱石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁要挑拨战争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逃不出咱们手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们两大领袖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指挥咱们斗争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的大旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要插遍全世界！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五○年一月）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正义的春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中苏新条约，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是正义的春天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真心又真意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如同是誓言；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水也有枯时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真心永不会枯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花也有谢时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真意永不会谢。 　（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两位好舵手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同御一只船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘风破海浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗亮闪闪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正义的春天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照在咱身边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力量大如山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗志响如雷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二月十七日）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}